                    (Verser) Customer Terms of Sale. Please refer to Verser Australia website for full details.<br>
                    Unless otherwise stated, all prices quoted are in Australian Dollar Currency(AUD) and are exclusive of GST, freight, and
                    configuration charges.<br>
                    Freight costs are based on standard road delivery.Air freight or any other form of special delivery will incur additional costs.<br>
                    Freight costs are based on standard road delivery.Air freight or any other form of special delivery will incur additional costs.<br>
                    xThe pricing specified above is not combinable with any other offer.<br>
                    Bundle pricing is subject to change in the event amendments are made to the quantity and/or bundle components
                    ordered.Please contact your account manager should you require changes to the bundle lines.<br>
